channel.title: [SRL] FreesGagility v1.5
channel.description:
Start in gnome agility in front of the log Make sure that you set laps and "nick field"
about 1 minute a lap is the average for this script now after v1.5 which is about 500 ms faster. will work on more speed later. hopefully no need for chat to be set to friends next update.
This was my first script. I have recently updated and it should give you some good runs. I personally do not use this script long term anymore so I need details about bugs.
Let me know of any bugs. Known Bugs -------------- timing issue with tree--Fixed Mine--Needs better tunnel in use detecting -- working on it [brain fart perhaps] --------------
v1.5 yet another rewrite and cuting out of useless code[1/2]. timing issues addressed.
v1.4 renewed interest in script needed massive update
